                 <span className="text-4xl font-black text-blue-400">₪{turnover.toLocaleString()}</span>
              </div>
              <input 
                type="range" 
                min="60000" 
                max="2000000" 
                step="10000"
                value={turnover}
                onChange={(e) => setTurnover(Number(e.target.value))}
                className="w-full h-4 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full appearance-none cursor-pointer accent-blue-500"
              />
              <div className="flex justify-between mt-6 text-gray-500 text-sm font-black italic">
                <span>₪60,000</span>
                <span>₪2,000,000+</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div className="space-y-6">
              <p className="text-xl font-black mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                <Zap className="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-400" />
                איזה ערוצים אנחנו מקימים לך?
